===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #17] id: assert-common-profile-restrictions
Section 4
Common restrictions on the IA Sequence for all profiles:
- The maximum size of an OBU SHALL be limited to 2MB.
- There SHALL be only one unique Codec Config OBU.
- num_sub_mixes SHOULD be set to 1.
- num_audio_elements SHOULD be set to at most 28.
- When num_layers = 1, both output_gain_is_present_flag and recon_gain_is_present_flag SHALL be set to 0.

